OL,3,CAll you need to know ahead of
OL,4,CCheltenham Festival 2026
OL,6,FFor those arriving by train, a shuttle
OL,7,Fbus will run between Cheltenham Spa
OL,8,Fstation, Cheltenham Town Centre and
OL,9,Fthe Racecourse with a return ticket
OL,10,Fcosting #9. Or, if you don't mind
OL,11,Fwalking, it takes less than an hour to
OL,12,Fget to the Festival on foot from the
OL,13,Fstation.
OL,15,FCheltenham Racecourse also operates
OL,16,Fthe busiest temporary airfield in the
OL,17,FUK, welcoming more than 400 helicopter
OL,18,Farrivals during Cheltenham festival
OL,19,Fweek.
OL,21,FWhere can I eat and drink?
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
