OL,3,CAll you need to know ahead of
OL,4,CCheltenham Festival 2026
OL,6,FLadies Day will return in 2026 after
OL,7,Fthe Festival officially changed the
OL,8,Fevent to 'Style Wednesday' in 2024.
OL,10,FAwards will be given to the Best
OL,11,FDressed, Best Dressed Duo, and Best
OL,12,FDressed Group with more than #10,000
OL,13,Fof prizes up for grabs.
OL,15,FFancy dress isn't permitted in
OL,16,FHospitality, restaurants or the Club
OL,17,FEnclosure during the Festival but is
OL,18,Fallowed in other areas so long as the
OL,19,Foutfit is not offensive.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
